  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>NEVER EVER</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Never Ever</l>
          <l>Never say forever</l>
          <l>Never Ever</l>
          <l>Never say forever</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>I never hear you saying like before</l>
          <l>The words I love you no one says no more</l>
          <l>Whatever happened to those simple words</l>
          <l>They disappeared like heaven and I feel that</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Never ever</l>
          <l>Never say forever</l>
          <l>Never ever</l>
          <l>Never say forever</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Stars are shining in the sky</l>
          <l>And in the moonlight you can never hide</l>
          <l>Try to look me in the eye</l>
          <l>And you’ll be mind tonight</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>(you) never stay to see the sun</l>
          <l>Always being on the run</l>
          <l>(you) make up stories just for fun</l>
          <l>No one ever told me that you’re so</l>
          <l>Clever…</l>
          <l>Ever…</l>
          <l>Never say forever</l>
          <l>Never ever</l>
          <l>Never say forever</l>
          <l>…</l>
          <l>You think you can fool me, but I know all about you!</l>
          <l>I know your game, I am playing it too.</l>
          <l>You see – I am the one holding the cards here.</l>
          <l>You think you are smart,</l>
          <l>You think you are - clever</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
